---
title: Garlic-Herb Meatballs & Red Pesto Risoni with Parmesan Cheese
description: Our red pesto – made with chargrilled capsicum, sun-dried tomatoes, parmesan, basil and garlic – puts a fun twist on this meatball risoni. Garnish it with parsley for an extra herby hit and grated Parmesan for a sharp bite. Bring all those elements together and you’ve got a filling dinner that delivers with every mouthful.
